Package: qtemplate
Title: Create quick standardised quarto template documents
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Simon", "Andrews", , "simon.andrews@babraham.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is designed for the Babraham Bioinformatics group but could be adpated elsewhere. It provides a set of standard quarto template documents into which you can substitute some basic information. I will allow you to get a new project off the ground quickly and easily.
License: GPL (>= 3) + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
